relatedmaterial.head: Related Materials at the New York University Archives

Washington Square Park (New York, NY) and Washington Square Area Image Collection, 1850-1990 (NYU.ARCH.PHOTO.00001)

odd.head: General Note
odd.p: This collection is oversized materials stored in 8 flat file cases and 7 oversized boxes stored on top of flat file 6. Cases 1-5 and 7 and 8 are in the front reading room and case 6 is in the rear of the Archives. All contents are described in the finding aid except Series VIII: posters and event fliers which are described in an Access database on the University Archives shared drive and cannot be accessed remotely.
